"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"There is a fragile ceasefire between the US and Iran, and they are trying to end a three-month war. But there are still hostilities happening.\",            \"english_title\": \"Fragile Ceasefire\",            \"translated_version\": \"Hay una tregua fr\u00e1gil entre Estados Unidos e Ir\u00e1n, y est\u00e1n tratando de terminar una guerra de tres meses. Pero todav\u00eda hay peleas.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Tregua Fr\u00e1gil\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"A 31-year-old Swiss man has been arrested by police. The areas around the station are closed off.\",            \"english_title\": \"Swiss Man Arrested\",            \"translated_version\": \"La polic\u00eda arrest\u00f3 a un hombre suizo de 31 a\u00f1os. Las \u00e1reas alrededor de la estaci\u00f3n est\u00e1n cerradas.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Hombre Suizo Arrestado\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The former US first lady said she was scared by Joe Biden's performance against Donald Trump.\",            \"english_title\": \"Former First Lady's Fear\",            \"translated_version\": \"La ex primera dama de Estados Unidos dijo que estaba asustada por c\u00f3mo Joe Biden actu\u00f3 contra Donald Trump.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Miedo de la Ex Primera Dama\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Several groups of women and children who were in a Syrian camp for years have come back in recent months.\",            \"english_title\": \"Return from Syrian Camp\",            \"translated_version\": \"Varios grupos de mujeres y ni\u00f1os que estuvieron en un campamento sirio por a\u00f1os han regresado en los \u00faltimos meses.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Regreso del Campamento Sirio\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The Israeli military told Lebanese people to leave about 17% of their country's land.\",            \"english_title\": \"Israeli Military Warning\",            \"translated_version\": \"El ej\u00e9rcito israel\u00ed dijo a los libaneses que se vayan de alrededor del 17% de la tierra de su pa\u00eds.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Advertencia del Ej\u00e9rcito Israel\u00ed\"        }    ]}"